  <h2>Mobile Site Plans</h2>


  <h3>Do It Yourself</h3>

  <p>YoMobi provides a free and easy solution for businesses and individuals to create a mobile-optimized website. With just a little technical skill and time, you can create your own mobile site and immediately reap the benefits that come from offering your customers a better and more interactive mobile experience.<p>
  <br/>
  <p>YoMobi's mission is to provide a comprehensive all-in-one mobile ecosystem that includes all the features you need to thrive in the booming mobile-commerce space, all with minimal, time, effort and cost.</p>
  <br/>

  <div class="plan-box">
    <h3>Standard Plan</h3>
    <h3>Cost:</h3>
    <ul>
      <li>Free</li>
    </ul>
    <h3>Features:</h3>
    <ul>
      <li>Free Hosting</li>
      <li>Free Domain ([yoursitename].yomobi.com)</li>
      <li>Free auto-redirect code to connect your desktop site to your mobile site</li>
      <li>Free SMS and E-Mail Blast capability<span class="notation-number">1</span></li>
      <li>Free Social Media Integration</li>
      <li>Free Click-to-Call Phone Widget</li>
      <li>Free Location Map with smartphone GPS navigation</li>
      <li>Unlimited Custom Pages, Categories, and Links</li>
      <li>RSS Feed Support</li>
      <li>Deactivation of Categories (to support seasonal items)</li>
      <li>Limited Site Customization</li>
      <li>Discrete mobile advertisement</li>
    </ul>
  </div>
  <div class="plan-box">
    <h3>Custom Plan (Coming July 2012)</h3>
    <h3>Cost (Introductory Price):</h3>
    <ul>
      <li>$5 per month</li>
      <li>$50 per year<span class="notation-number">2</span></li>
    </ul>
    <h3>Features:</h3>
    <ul>
      <li>All the features included in the Standard Plan, plus:</li>
      <li>Custom Domain (m.yourdomain.com)</li>
      <li>Enhanced Site Customization</li>
      <li>No advertisements (available now, with payment)</li>
    </ul>
  </div>
<div class="hr"></div>
<div>
  <h3>Let YoMobi Build Your Site For You</h3>
  <p>Even though the YoMobi platform is so easy that you can do it yourself with minimal effort using content from your existing desktop website or facebook page, we realize how busy business owners are, so we're happy to get you started by building your site for you. We offer a lot of value for a very low price because our goal is to make the mobile-commerce space accessible to everyone.</p>
  <h3>Consulting Fees:</h3>
  <ul>
  <li>$25 flat fee to build a standard site<span class="notation-number">3</span></li>
  <li>$25 per hour for additional pages</li>
  </ul>
  <p>A typical site takes 2 to 4 hours depending on the number of pages and products/services uploaded. If you would like us to build your site please contact us at <a href="mailto:support@yomobi.com">support@yomobi.com</a>. Once we are done building your site, we will transfer ownership of the site to you. We can also provide training on how to optimally use and manage your site for the standard consulting rate.</p>
  <br/>
  <p>Once a site is created, updates take only minutes and you will be able to continue to maintain it very easily on your own.
  </p>
</div>

