<li>A standard site includes the following pages and features: About Us, Call Us (one-click calling), Find Us (interactive map with smartphone GPS navigation), Business Hours, Coupon, Keep Me Informed, Leave a Message, Call Me Back, and links to your desktop website, facebook page and twitter accounts, if applicable.</li>
